course.subject: TEMG
course.name: Special Project: “T&M Prototyping and Desktop Research” sponsored by UBS and Harman
course.description: UBS is the largest Swiss banking institution and largest private bank in the world with 160 years of history. Apart from private banking, UBS provides wealth management, asset management, and investment banking services for private, corporate, and institutional clients with international service. UBS manages the largest amount of private wealth in the world, counting approximately half of the world's billionaires among its clients. This Winter, UBS Asia Pacific regional teams will sponsor 3 topics with project sponsors from Equity Derivatives Trading, Quant Analytics and Digital Platforms groups. This course is for T&M-DDP students only. Enrollment in the project course requires approval of the course instructor.
